# LearnMore Frontend - Cursor Rules

## Project Overview
This is a space-themed educational platform built with Next.js 15. The frontend connects to a Go backend API.

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 15 (App Router)
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- Axios for API calls
- Zustand for state management
- Monaco Editor for code editing
- Framer Motion for animations

## Design Theme
- Space/cosmic theme with dark backgrounds
- Color palette: Deep blues (#0a0f1c), purples (#1a0a2e), cyan accents (#00d4ff), green highlights (#00ff88)
- Glassmorphism effects for cards/panels
- Subtle star animations in backgrounds
- Clean, minimal UI with space-inspired elements

## Code Style Guidelines
- Use TypeScript strict mode
- Functional components with hooks
- Custom hooks for reusable logic
- API calls through centralized axios instance in src/lib/api.ts
- Tailwind for styling (no CSS modules)
- Use 'use client' directive only when necessary
- Keep components modular and reusable
- ALWAYS check for existing files before creating new ones - update if exists, create if not
- NEVER create duplicate files in different locations

